<p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Computer-Vision-Algorithms-Applications-Science/dp/1848829345/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=Computer+Vision%3A+Algorithms+and+Applications&amp;qid=1555168737&amp;s=books&amp;sr=1-1"><strong>Computer Vision: Algorithms and Applications (CVAA)</strong></a>, 2011th Edition, Richard Szeliski</p>

<ul>
