<p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Introduction-Expert-Systems-Peter-Jackson/dp/0201876868/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=Introduction+to+Expert+Systems&amp;qid=1555042560&amp;s=books&amp;sr=1-1"><strong>Introduction to Expert Systems</strong></a>, 3rd Edition, Jackson P., Addison Wesley</p>

