<p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Category-Computer-Scientists-Foundations-Computing-ebook/dp/B00MG7E5WE/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=Basic+Theory+for+Computer+Scientists&amp;qid=1555123183&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-1"><strong>Basic Category Theory for Computer Scientists</strong></a>, 1991, Benjamin C. Pierce</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>é€‚ç”¨äººç¾¤:</strong> <em>freshmen</em></li>
